      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project seekers! This vehicle is ready for a transformation and offers a fantastic opportunity for someone looking for a budget-friendly project car. While it has seen better days and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention to get back to its best, it\u2019s a great starting point for a mechanic or a dedicated hobbyist. Grab this bargain and make it your own today!",
